---
const pageTitle = "BADINGA Technologies | Secure AI Platforms for Regulated & Disconnected Environments";
const pageDescription =
  "We help mid-size defense and government-adjacent organizations deploy AI-ready Kubernetes platforms on-prem—securely, auditable, and without relying on public cloud.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg?v=2" />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
  </head>


  <body>
    <main class="page">
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">BADINGA Technologies</p>

        <h1>Secure AI Platforms for Regulated &amp; Disconnected Environments</h1>

        <p class="subhead">
          We help mid-size defense and government-adjacent organizations deploy AI-ready Kubernetes
          platforms on-prem—securely, auditable, and without relying on public cloud.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="cta-primary" href="#contact">Request a Platform Assessment</a>
          <a class="cta-secondary" href="#what-we-do">See how we help</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="what-we-do" class="section">
        <h2>Your reality</h2>

        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>AI stuck in pilot</h3>
            <p>
              You have models or analytics initiatives, but no secure, production-ready platform to
              deploy them in restricted or disconnected environments.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Infrastructure risk</h3>
            <p>
              Your on-prem infrastructure is fragile, hard to audit, and tightly coupled to tribal
              knowledge—making modernization risky and slow.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>No platform ownership</h3>
            <p>
              Teams are stretched thin. ML engineers do infrastructure work, infrastructure teams
              block AI, and no one owns the full system end-to-end.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>A secure, AI-ready platform—delivered end-to-end</h2>

        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Hardened Kubernetes for on-prem and disconnected environments</li>
          <li>AI/ML inference pipelines (no black-box SaaS dependencies)</li>
          <li>MLOps &amp; LLMOps designed for auditability and control</li>
          <li>Clear architecture, documentation, and handover</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="outcome">
          <strong>Outcome:</strong> A platform you can operate, explain, and defend.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Why BADINGA Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We focus on execution, not experimentation. Our work is designed for regulated
          environments where security, traceability, and reliability matter more than hype.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="section contact">
        <h2>Request a Platform Assessment</h2>
        <p>
          A focused engagement to evaluate your infrastructure, security constraints, and AI
          readiness.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <p class="contact-line">
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:contact@badinga.tech">contact@badinga.tech</a>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-line">Location: United States (remote engagements)</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="footer">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} BADINGA Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>

    <style>
      :global(body) {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #0b1220;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .page {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 20px 72px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 44px 28px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.75);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.2vw, 3rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .subhead {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
        max-width: 70ch;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .cta-primary,
      .cta-secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.14);
      }

      .cta-primary {
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .cta-secondary {
        background: #ffffff;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.92);
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 44px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.82);
      }

      .bullets {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      .bullets li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .outcome {
        margin-top: 14px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border-left: 4px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.35);
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .contact-box {
        border: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.03);
        max-width: 620px;
      }

      .contact-line {
        margin: 6px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        padding-top: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.12);
        color: rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.65);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
